detaileddescription.para: Unit tests covering UHF_Task.c file that includes functions for cyclic tasks and initialization. It also includes functionality of the module which is to receive message over a CCAN from SAM, marge those messages into internal structures and send depending on payload type( performed event - FFB press or kessy event) to FDH or to KESSY.
